These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
City: liverpool, miami, rome, nizza
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, soy-milk, 7up
There are 4 different nationalities: german, chinese, spanish, pakistani
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, marigold, bellflower, begonia
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, ritmeester, dannemann, fonseca
 1. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the pakistani is between the person traveling to liverpool and the fonseca-smoker##2
 3. the person who growspoppy is the fonseca-smoker##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
 5. the dunhill-smoker is between the person traveling to liverpool and the spanish##2
 6. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is the person traveling to rome##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
10. the german is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| City           | rome | liverpool   | nizza | miami |
| Beverage   | juice      | lemonade | soy-milk              | 7up |
| Nationality   | german       | chinese     | pakistani               | spanish    |
| Flower           | marigold        | bellflower     | begonia           | poppy       |
| Cigar     | ritmeester | dannemann     | dunhill                | fonseca      |

