4 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, canasta, billiard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, mystery, sports, disaster
 1. the tower house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 2. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 3. the palace house is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person playing snooker##2
 4. the person who growsaconite is the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person playing canasta is the palace house##1
 6. the tower house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 7. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the tower house##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the craftsman house##1
10. the tower house is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
11. the person watching animation movies is the person who's birthday is in october##1
12. the person who's birthday is in february is the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Birthday          | october       | march      | february      | january      |
| House           | futuristic | palace | tower | craftsman |
| Flower   | aconite          | orchid       | bellflower            | dahlia      |
