 8. the person driving the roller is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is the montecristo-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

