City: miami, berlin, boston, hamburg
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, colonial, cottage
 1. the colonial house is the swisher-smoker##1
 2. the gothic-revival house is between the person watching western movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
 3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 4. the owner of the horse is the person traveling to miami##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is between the person traveling to miami and the art-deco house##2
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the owner of the lizard is the cottage house##1
 9. the owner of the rat is between the gothic-revival house and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
10. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left##1
11. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
