 4. the ranch-style house is the person playing go##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person playing domino##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is the person traveling to new-york##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 8. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 9. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person who growsrose is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the owner of the mouse is between the person playing domino and the gothic-revival house##2
12. the owner of the turtle is between the ranch-style house and the person traveling to new-york##2

.:: Answer ::.
